descriptionHtml:
A pair of archer's to keep the wolves of your back while you are on your adventures. Alexia and Elli are waiting in the Sleaping Giant in Riverwood. apachiihair is required. Thank you apachii for the great mod and permission to use it. Also thank you to my wife for letting me invade her game with my minions to test them.
I'm new at this and suggestions are always welcome.
They will be nude when you meet but will equip their gear when recruited.
author: wachie61
